Group B Streptococci Screening Before Repeat Cesarean Delivery: A 
Cost-Effectiveness Analysis.

Albright CM(1), MacGregor C, Sutton D, Theva M, Hughes BL, Werner EF.

Author information:
(1)Division of Maternal-Fetal Medicine, Department of Obstetrics and Gynecology, 
